Current Mods

1. Screen lens and Higher Resolution Adapter for the Current V1 Model
    For this modification, you will need two 3X lenses. Here is the AliExpress link: https://es.aliexpress.com/item/1005007851751430.html?spm=a2g0o.cart.0.0.1b427a9dTN1Vnf&mp=1&pdp_npi=5%40dis%21EUR%21EUR%2047.18%21EUR%2023.59%21%21EUR%2023.59%21%21%21%40210391a017556333335244487ef897%2112000042539503501%21ct%21ES%21939915184%21%212%210&gatewayAdapt=glo2esp
    You will also need two 0.39" 1026x768 OLED displays: https://es.aliexpress.com/item/1005004141499765.html?spm=a2g0o.cart.0.0.1b427a9dTN1Vnf&mp=1&pdp_npi=5%40dis%21EUR%21EUR%2067.38%21EUR%2061.99%21%21EUR%2061.99%21%21%21%40211b61a417556337067818628e2f29%2112000042533315985%21ct%21ES%21939915184%21%212%210&gatewayAdapt=glo2esp

    This mod is worth your time, as it can lower the price range for both the binocular and mono versions of the NVG. In addition, the higher-resolution displays can help with target acquisition and navigation.

